title: VTech® Go! Go! Smart Wheels® Ultimate RC Speedway™ Commercial :30
description: Zip around the VTech Go! Go! Smart Wheels Ultimate RC Speedway, and speed through four action zones and over nine SmartPoint® locations. Use the steering wheel-shaped remote control for an exciting interactive experience with the RC SmartPoint® Racer! The speedway is 4.5 feet wide and includes 13.5 feet of interchangeable tracks, a stunt ramp, elevator, movable gears, starting flags and track switches that are all triggered by the RC race car.
